<!-- Button trigger modal -->
<button type="button" class="btn mr-1 px-2 py-1" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#itemPoolModal">
<i class="bi bi-question-circle"></i>
</button>

<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal" id="itemPoolModal" tabindex="-1">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h1 class="modal-title fs-5">Item pool</h1>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>This setting affects the amount of ammo and tanks which may be placed:</p>

        <ul>
        <li><strong>Full</strong>: 46 Missile packs, 10 Super packs, 10 Power Bomb packs, 14 Energy Tanks, 4 Reserve Tanks
        <li><strong>Reduced</strong>: 12 Missile packs, 6 Super packs, 6 Power Bomb packs, 3 Energy Tanks, 3 Reserve Tanks
        </ul>

        <p>Using a reduced amount of ammo and tanks causes some item locations to be missing an item. Regardless of the item pool settings, extra Energy Tanks may be added to ensure the game is beatable based on selected difficulty settings.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>




